Data from kaggle at https://www.kaggle.com/stefanoleone992/fifa-20-complete-player-dataset

Background:
This note book is was created in March 2023. Newcastle United recently advertised for a data and insights manager, which looked an interesting post, one of the key roles of the post is to get insight into the transfer market. I know next to nothing about team sports, including football and less about transfer markets. So this nootbook is part of a journey into understanding sports data.

